Details

See the code books in the CodeBooks folder for details. The CodeBooks folder is a top level folder of the PDS package. To see where the PDS package is installed on your machine, type the following at the R prompt: system.file(package = "PDS")

Examples

dim(gapminder)
#> [1] 213  16
